```

**was:** Beginning [was]. Love [was there]. Fear [was there].
> *Where it began: with love and fear together. You remember the origin clearly now.*

**now:** Beginning. Love. Fear.
> *Beginning right now. Love is here. Fear is here. Both arising simultaneously in this moment.*

**wil:** Beginning [will come]. Love [will arise]. Fear [will arise].
