#### 8. The Recognition
```limn
you kno | rem cla | pat fam
```

**was:** You knew [then]. Remembered clear[ly]. Pattern familiar.
> *You knew this. You remembered it clearly. The pattern was familiar - you'd been here before.*

**now:** You know. Remembering clear[ly]. Pattern familiar.
> *You know this. You are remembering. The pattern is familiar. Recognition is happening now.*

**wil:** You will know. Will remember clear[ly]. Pattern [will be] familiar.
