#### 9. ★ The Mirror Phrase
```limn
sel see | oth see | sam dif
```

**was:** Self saw [itself]. Other saw [you]. Same [but] different [then].
> *You saw yourself. Someone else saw you. You were the same person but looked different in their eyes. Past perspective.*

**now:** Self sees. Other sees. Same [but] different.
> *You see yourself. Other sees you. Same being, different perspectives. Both true now.*

**wil:** Self will see. Other will see. Same [but] different.
> *You will see yourself. Other will see you. Will you be the same? Will you be different?*

---

#### 10. The Choice Point
```limn
