```

**was:** Path [was] three. Key held. Story changed.
> *There were three paths. You held a key. The story changed because of which key you chose.*

**now:** Path three. Key hold. Story changes.
> *Three paths exist now. You hold a key. The story is changing based on your choice.*

**wil:** Path [will be] three. Key [will] hold. Story [will] change.
> *Three paths will open. You will hold a key. The story will change based on which you choose.*

